{"seeAlsoSections":[{"anchor":"Writing-Rules","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Rule","doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Rules","doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Intent","doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Command","doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/say(_:)","doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/refuse(_:)","doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/reply(_:)","doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/end(won:)"],"title":"Writing Rules","generated":true}],"metadata":{"title":"Writing Rules","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"Gnusto"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Attach game logic to items, locations, and the world."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Rules are where a game stops being a map of static rooms and starts reacting. A rule is a phase (when it runs), an owner (what it watches), an optional set of intents (which actions it cares about), and a body of ordinary Swift that reads and writes the live world.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Every rule lives in a game’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rules"},{"type":"text","text":" block, which yields a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Rules","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" value:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["var rules: Rules {","    cloak.after(.take, .wear)  { bar.isLit = false }","    bar.beforeEachTurn         { … }","    world.after(.go)           { … }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This guide is a catalogue of what you can attach and how the bodies read state. For the order rules fire in, see ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/TheTurnPipeline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Choose an owner and a phase","anchor":"Choose-an-owner-and-a-phase","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A rule is created by a factory method on the thing it watches. Three owners are available:"}]},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Owner","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Factories"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Item","isActive":true}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"before"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"after"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Location","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"before","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"after","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"beforeEachTurn","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"afterEachTurn","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"onEnter","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/World","type":"reference","isActive":true}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"before"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"after"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"beforeEachTurn","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"afterEachTurn","type":"codeVoice"}]}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"before(_:perform:)"},{"type":"text","text":" runs before the default action, for the listed intents. Veto the action with "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/refuse(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":", or handle it yourself with "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/reply(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"after(_:perform:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" runs after the default action succeeded, for the listed intents. React to what happened."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"beforeEachTurn"},{"text":" \/ ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"afterEachTurn"},{"text":" run on ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"every","type":"text"}]},{"text":" turn spent in the location (or, on ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"world"},{"text":", everywhere) regardless of intent — the home for daemons and timers. ","type":"text"},{"code":"afterEachTurn","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" runs even on refused turns, because world time still passes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onEnter"},{"text":" (locations only) runs the moment the player arrives, just before the room is auto-described.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Match specific intents","anchor":"Match-specific-intents"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The intents you pass to "},{"code":"before","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"code":"after","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" filter the rule. List one or several; list none to match every action."}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Only when the player tries to take OR wear the cloak:","cloak.before(.take, .wear) { … }","","\/\/ On any action targeting the statue:","statue.before() { say(\"The statue's eyes seem to follow you.\") }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The built-in intents are constants on "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Intent","isActive":true},{"text":" (","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Intent\/take"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Intent\/drop"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Intent\/examine"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Intent\/go"},{"text":", and so on). Custom verbs mint their own — ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Intent(\"ring\")"},{"text":" — which you match the same way. See ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/AddingCustomVerbs"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Read-and-write-live-state","level":2,"text":"Read and write live state"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Inside a rule body, your declarations "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"are","type":"text"}]},{"text":" the live entities. The bare identifiers ","type":"text"},{"code":"player","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"command","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"world","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and every room and item you declared resolve to the current turn’s state.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Items expose "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Item\/isHeld"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Item\/isWorn"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Item\/isTouched"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Item\/name"},{"type":"text","text":", a settable "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Item\/description"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Item\/holds(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":", and the movers "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Item\/move(to:)"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Item\/vanish()"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["lever.after(.take) {","    say(\"It comes loose in your hand.\")","    trapdoor.description = \"The trapdoor now stands open.\"","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Locations expose a settable ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Location\/isLit","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Location\/isVisited","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Location\/contains(_:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Location\/name","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", and a settable ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Location\/description","type":"reference"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["cloak.after(.drop, .putOn) { bar.isLit = true }"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The player exposes a settable "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Player\/location"},{"type":"text","text":" (assigning teleports without describing the destination), a settable "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Player\/score"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Player\/moves"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Player\/isCarrying(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Player\/isWearing(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["message.before(.read) {","    player.score += 1","    say(message.description)","    try end(won: true)","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The command being performed is available as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"command"},{"type":"text","text":" ("},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Command","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"): its "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Command\/intent","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Command\/directObject","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Command\/indirectObject","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Command\/direction","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Command\/preposition","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", and the raw "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Command\/verbPhrase","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" the player typed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["bar.beforeEachTurn {","    guard !bar.isLit else { return }","    if command.intent == .go, command.direction == .north { return }","    try refuse(\"Blundering around in the dark isn't a good idea!\")","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For state the engine doesn’t already track — a wallet, an item’s price, a creature’s HP — reach for a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/Global","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or a custom trait. See "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/CustomStateAndTraits","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Produce-output-and-control-the-turn","level":2,"text":"Produce output and control the turn"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Four free functions are available in any rule body:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/say(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" — add a line to the turn’s output and keep going. The default action still runs."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/refuse(_:)"},{"text":" — print a complaint and abort the action (and remaining rules).","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Gnusto\/documentation\/Gnusto\/reply(_:)","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" — print a response ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"in place of"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" the default action. Same mechanics as ","type":"text"},{"code":"refuse","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", different intent: use it when your rule is the behavior, not a veto.","type":"text"}]}]},{"conten